### 🧠 LLM Knowledge Assistant

**RAG-powered system for intelligent document querying**

```text
User Query
   ↓
Embedding → Vector DB (Pinecone)
   ↓
Context Retrieval
   ↓
LLM (Grounded Response)
   ↓
Answer
```

